  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a bonus action, you cause a psychic disturbance around the target cursed by your @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-spells.xr8TQuchvLqaKeOt]{Hex} spell or by a warlock feature of yours, such as @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.R7KO3rSiHZMJIyfX]{Hexblade's Curse} and @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.tejEUCzkm3R8aWtL]{Sign of Ill Omen}. When you do so, you deal psychic damage to the cursed target and each creature of your choice within 5 feet of it. The psychic damage equals your Charisma modifier (minimum of 1 damage). To use this invocation, you must be able to see the cursed target, and it must be within 30 feet of you.</p>",
